message.body: I'm in Baltimore! I've been traveling like a crazy lady. How are you!
Lol good. Daniel Ceren and I went to Jeff's show. Daniel picked out my outfit ha!
Awesome. That sounds fun. What did he pick out?
We went to trident before. I just ran into them on newbury after work. We talked a lot about my thesis. I may hold off on thesis advisor until I get thru writing with Jan and Gunta
Oh nice. Did Daniel recommend that?
No. I just don't know if I'd like to work with Nicole. Daniel challenged me to think more about how I view photo or use photo and how that translates into my thesis
Brian and Jan thought it would be good.
Nicole? Was she assigned to you?
On an unrelated note, I really like Nicole. She had great feedback for everyone! I was impressed with her as a reviewer.
She's a smart and quick lady.
Daniel made me use paper and pen not my camera at Jeff's show. It was a weird experiment but interesting
Did you and Ingrid wear matching dresses ha! I saw on fb
We tried them on at a store with very flattering lights!
